'''INFP'''（内倾/直觉/情感/理解）是[[迈尔斯·布里格斯性格分类法|迈尔斯·布里格斯性格分类法]]中十六种人格类型之一，在[[柯尔塞气质类型测试|柯尔塞气质类型测试]]中被称为'''[[治疗者_(角色变异)|治療師]]'''，属于[[理想者_(气质类型)|理想者]]的四种类型之一。<ref name=foundation>{{cite web|url=http://www.myersbriggs.org/my-mbti-personality-type/mbti-basics/the-16-mbti-types.asp|title=Myers-Briggs Foundation: The 16 MBTI Types|accessdate=2011-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090513191631/http://www.myersbriggs.org/my-mbti-personality-type/mbti-basics/the-16-mbti-types.asp|archive-date=2009-05-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

INFP大概占人口的1%-5%。<ref name=Keirsey>{{cite web|url=http://www.keirsey.com/handler.aspx?s=keirsey&f=fourtemps&tab=3&c=healer|title=Keirsey.com Portrait of the Healer|accessdate=2011-02-02|archive-date=2010-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101031055338/http://keirsey.com/handler.aspx?s=keirsey&f=fourtemps&tab=3&c=healer|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capt.org/mbti-assessment/estimated-frequencies.htm|title=CAPT|accessdate=2011-02-02|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911215111/https://www.capt.org/mbti-assessment/estimated-frequencies.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

